{"id": "1431432757392969768", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "722017209182060635", "author_name": "esukun125", "author_bot": false, "content": "本当に大体ですが、60レベステージで最上級素材が20～25個くらいずつドロップだったはずです　これはソレールイベもリリーイベもあんま変わらなかったと記憶しているので次来るとしてもあまり変わらないと思います", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T00:02:44.097000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431433276001746975", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "722017209182060635", "author_name": "esukun125", "author_bot": false, "content": "(でも次くるイベはBOXガチャじゃね、という話は上がってます　トゥルーイベとマーフィーイベが同じ形式だから次はダフォイベと同じ形式のが来るかもね、と)", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T00:04:47.743000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431456492849987764", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "302789553612128256", "author_name": "mazerice", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます、今スタミナ120当たり金券ショップの素材交換レートで紫素材40個分になってるので、やっぱりだいぶ効率は良いですよね、、\n(もちろん日毎の交換上限はありますが)", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T01:37:03.071000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431457445477089370", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "302789553612128256", "author_name": "mazerice", "author_bot": false, "content": "ちなみに1キャラの才能上げ切るのにどれくらいお金かかるか分かる方いますか？\n手持ちの薬剤を6割ほどぶっ込んで金券いま2000万ぐらいあるんですが、これでも全然足りないくらいならこのまま貯蓄しとこうかな、、", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T01:40:50.195000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431493522577428560", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "真にお金かかるのは、密約厳選なので、カツカツでやってると後で泣きを見ます。\n\n才能はめっちゃコストかかるし費用対効果考えたら後回しがいいかと", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T04:04:11.646000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["302789553612128256"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431457445477089370", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431498225361358970", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "302789553612128256", "author_name": "mazerice", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど、才能より密約のが優先度高めなんですね\n参考までにどれくらいの基準で厳選してるか伺ってもいいですか？\n大体の部位にダメ強0.75以上を目安に付けて、以降はキリがないので確実に恩恵受けれる才能を先に上げようかなーと思ってました", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T04:22:52.877000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["797509921343275038"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431493522577428560", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431500848453648488", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "722017209182060635", "author_name": "esukun125", "author_bot": false, "content": "一応質問に答える分として、わたしがマーフィー待機してたときに全てを一から上げるために集めてた、素材の数置いておきます　賢者の石だけ間違ってるんでもうちょっと必要です()", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T04:33:18.271000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1431500848248258671", "filename": "IMG_5489.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 21603, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1431500848248258671/IMG_5489.png?ex=6a341dce&is=6a32cc4e&hm=48631925f80ebc2bbb62fa199a3f8123cb4a767e7ed420804b0affca8dd9cd6f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431501245008449546", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "722017209182060635", "author_name": "esukun125", "author_bot": false, "content": "でも密約優先したほうがいいのはホントです！\n自分もダメきょ0.75とあと死亡抵抗もついでに付いたらいいなを意識して厳選してました", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T04:34:52.817000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["302789553612128256"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431498225361358970", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431501553495445595", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "722017209182060635", "author_name": "esukun125", "author_bot": false, "content": "あと才能上げきるのに金券もそうですが週ボス素材70と賢者の石5？くらい要求されるのでそっちのが痛いです()", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T04:36:06.366000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙇", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431502696761790655", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "589932567323607102", "author_name": "hiroshi0000", "author_bot": false, "content": "密約転写は運が悪いと数百万くらいスッと溶けたこともあるので、ダメ強0.75〜0.9あたりで一度転写しておくのはいいなと思いました　出ない時は出なかった……", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T04:40:38.942000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-25T04:58:08.528000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431543187066978374", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "おすすめとしてはランダムぶん回して強化1〜\n\nそこを固定→抵抗いい数値つくまで\n\nを頑張ればこれくらいに", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T07:21:32.583000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["302789553612128256"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1431543186404409514", "filename": "IMG_5824.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 186220, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1431543186404409514/IMG_5824.jpg?ex=6a34453c&is=6a32f3bc&hm=8bcc51906120617e98ee9a26ae6ae1d5d20ad05c6305cb68e97f4df6918e7cb5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431498225361358970", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431543266037334087", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "煮詰まってくると1箇所更新に数百万かかります。", "timestamp": "2025-10-25T07:21:51.411000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙇", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
